reviewText: Great movies for the price can't complain.
Great deal for both movies and you don't have a 3D setup.  Other than that it is what it is, 1 good remake and 1 laughable...

These movies are both horror movies that get you to jump or cringe.  Even though these movies are clearly made to be in 3D, they are still fine without the 3D.  There is nudity and topless scenes in both of these movies so parents be warned, the R rating is not just for language and violence.

I bought the separate additions for my mom and both were great quality, but on the expensive side. The Alliance entertainment versions are just as good as the original. The only difference in these and the USA release is that it has FRENCH on the other side.
